      • drive

        public void drive(double leftspeed,
         double rightspeed)
        Set the output for both motors
        Parameters:
        leftspeed - double ranging from -1.0 to 1.0, adding anything higher or lower will not cause errors and will automatically be adjusted
        rightspeed - double ranging from -1.0 to 1.0, adding anything higher or lower will not cause errors and will automatically be adjusted. Right Motor is inverted and the Victor can only be inverted directly in the output.
